OL,3,COscar-nominated director Coralie
OL,4,CFargeat on the anger that fuelled The
OL,5,CSubstance
OL,7,FCoralie Fargeat tells Arts Editor Nina
OL,8,FNannar it's 'truly terrifying' how few
OL,9,Fwomen have been awarded the top prizes
OL,10,Fin filmmaking.
OL,12,FIt was when filmmaker Coralie Fargeat
OL,13,Fwas approaching her late forties, and
OL,14,Fthinking about her future in the
OL,15,Findustry that she decided to tackle
OL,16,Fthe issue of ageism and sexism head on.
