OL,3,COscar-nominated director Coralie
OL,4,CFargeat on the anger that fuelled The
OL,5,CSubstance
OL,7,FThe Substance, filmed in her native
OL,8,FParis, deals with a TV star played by
OL,9,FDemi Moore, who is deemed too old for
OL,10,Fthe screen by her sexist boss, who
OL,11,Fwants someone younger.
OL,13,FThe role has given Moore, now 62, her
OL,14,Ffirst Golden Globe award and now her
OL,15,Ffirst Oscar nomination. It has made
OL,16,Fdirector Fargeat only the eighth woman
OL,17,Fto ever get a best director nomination
OL,18,Fin the Oscars' 97 year history. Only
OL,19,Fthree women have ever won that award.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/5
