OL,3,COscar-nominated director Coralie
OL,4,CFargeat on the anger that fuelled The
OL,5,CSubstance
OL,7,FIn taking aim at ageism and sexism,
OL,8,FFargeat does not hold back. The anger
OL,9,Fis visible in the scenes of true body
OL,10,Fhorror, it is visually a stunning
OL,11,Fachievement that has also put The
OL,12,FSubstance in the running for best film
OL,13,Fat next month's awards.
OL,15,FShe is of course dismayed at the
OL,16,Fstatistics that show the
OL,17,Funderrepresentation of women at
OL,18,FHollywood's top table, male directors
OL,19,Fwere overwhelmingly behind the biggest
OL,20,Fbox office hits of the last year. It's
OL,21,Fnot like we are less skilled, she says.
