OL,3,COscar-nominated director Coralie
OL,4,CFargeat on the anger that fuelled The
OL,5,CSubstance
OL,7,FThe problems are so deep rooted, the
OL,8,Fidea that big budgets, big power
OL,9,Fequate with men in Hollywood.
OL,11,FHer film is loud she says, violent and
OL,12,Fin your face because that's what the
OL,13,Fissue takes these days. Whatever
OL,14,Fhappens at next month's Oscars, the
OL,15,Findustry is taking note of a director
OL,16,Fwith a lot to say, and the boldness to
OL,17,Fdeliver her message her own way.
OL,19,FWhat Coralie does next will be
OL,20,Finteresting.
